'''Agapos the Eighth''' was a [[Gender/Legends|male]] ruler of the [[Sunesi]]. While popular among his subjects, history would show him to be largely ineffective&mdash;it was during his tenure that the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] managed to establish a hold on [[Monor II]]. When the [[Agapos the Ninth|heir to the throne]] showed latent [[The Force/Legends|Force]] talents, Agapos the Eighth stepped down and retired in seclusion.

